data.description: Solid 4 bedroom/1.75 bath, 2,858 square foot brick rancher w/2 car attached garage in quiet neighborhood. 3 bedrooms/1.75 bath on main floor with 2 additional bedrooms and family room in the basement. The kitchen was updated in the 90's and all appliances stay. Oak floors on the main floor bedrooms and fireplaces on main floor and in basement. Gas furnace and gas water heater. Home sits on a level .89 acres with fenced backyard and a 320 SF pole barn for extra storage. The lot is wide and deep enough that it could possibly be subdivided for another home or duplex to be built behind the current home. West Valley Schools.
